In fact, this is where we'll likely
spend the majority of our time.

3
00:00:06,830 --> 00:00:10,050
This is the user interacting through
some interface to accomplish some task.

4
00:00:10,050 --> 00:00:13,220
That's what we mean by
the predictor model of the user.

5
00:00:13,220 --> 00:00:16,720
The user is actively involved in looking
at the task, making predictions about

6
