7
00:00:19,300 --> 00:00:22,870
This is where we looked at the gulf of
execution and the gulf of evaluation.

8
00:00:22,870 --> 00:00:25,010
How hard is is for
the user to interact with a task?

9
00:00:25,010 --> 00:00:28,520
And how hard is it for them to get
feedback on their interaction?

10
00:00:28,520 --> 00:00:31,530
